    • spawnBackground

      protected void spawnBackground​(int x, int width, java.lang.String world)
      Spawn a background image starting at x and a bifrost split.
      Parameters:
      x - starting coordinate
      width - width of the image using scaleWidth(width)
      world - world type, must match the first word of a .png file in assets/images/Backgrounds/'world'_bg.png, any information after an underscore in world is ignored i.e. asgard and asgard_3 are both the same.

    • spawnMapChunk

      protected void spawnMapChunk​(int[] x, int y, java.lang.String type, java.lang.String world)
      Spawn a line of 'type' at x[0], x[1], ..., x[n] having only a single collision entity that spans from x[0] to the end of the map chunk at x[n + 3].

      On disposal of the single collision entity, all map pieces created are disposed of.

      Parameters:
      x - game x coordinates to spawn floors at
      y - game y coordinates to spawn floors at
      type - type of map piece, should only be either 'floor' or 'platform'
      world - the world type to load in. Must match the name of a .png file in assets/images/worlds (e.g. assets/images/worlds/world.png)
